SIMPLE: subdelegate
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Subdelegate
<hw>Sub*del"e*gate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A subordinate
delegate, or one with inferior powers.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Subdelegate</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Subdelegate
<hw>Sub*del"e*gate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To appoint
to act as subdelegate, or as a subordinate; to depete.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Subdented</ent>⟦br⟧
